T1  - Adapting to Radical Change: The Benefits of Short-Horizon Investors
AU  - Giannetti, Mariassunta
AU  - Yu, Xiaoyun
Y1  - 2020/10/06
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3702
