T1  - Social Learning in the COVID-19 Pandemic: Community Establishments’ Closure Decisions Follow Those of Nearby Chain Establishments
AU  - de Vaan, Mathijs
AU  - Mumtaz, Saqib
AU  - Nagaraj, Abhishek
AU  - Srivastava, Sameer B.
Y1  - 2021/05/20
